stories.title: Pathan reprimanded following ICC Code of Conduct Breach
stories.summary: Indian fast bowler Irfan Pathan has been reprimanded for a breach of the International Cricket Council's (ICC) Code of Conduct following a gesture towards Australian batsman Damien Martyn in the deciding VB Series final at the Sydney Cricket Ground

stories.title: Different class
stories.subTitle: Australia v India, VB Series, 2nd final, Sydney
stories.summary: One-day cricket demands a different set of skills, both physical and mental, and Australia, on the evidence of the two finals, are light years ahead of India
stories.byline: The Wisden Verdict by Sambit Bal

stories.title: Imperious Australia crush India by 208 runs
stories.subTitle: Australia v India, VB Series, 2nd final, Sydney
stories.summary: Matthew Hayden set the tone, Andrew Symonds delivered the knockout punch, and the bowlers added insult to injury as Australia romped to an emphatic 208-run victory
stories.byline: The Wisden Bulletin by S Rajesh
